title: I Know it's Normals but...

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body: This is NOT ok in the slightest. Sure, they have the obviously superior team in terms of rankings but hey! it's normals right! Except the two unrankeds on my team have < 100 games. Great stuff. Real fun. Also darius admitted he was a diamond smurf premade with yasuo and draven to get easier matches. Him bming me all game is still on my mind.
